name: SustainDAO
description:
The world's first DAO to make Bitcoin sustainable. We are uniting miners, maxis, investors, crypto anons and degens, eco-frens, and climate KOLs to make bitcoin the most sustainable reserve asset class in the world!

We believe that a rising tide lifts all boats - greening BTC will drive the whole industry forward!
payDisclosure: Paying SustainDAO is not an investment, it is a way to support the project. Any value or utility of the token you receive is determined by SustainDAO.
